      <title>哈里斯称她稍后将考虑乌克兰加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/harris-says-she-ll-weigh-ukraine-nato-membership-at-later-point</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党总统候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯拒绝透露当选后是否会支持乌克兰加入北约，但她发誓，她将坚持让基辅领导人参与美国与弗拉基米尔·普京就结束持续冲突进行的任何谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/harris-says-she-ll-weigh-ukraine-nato-membership-at-later-point</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中情局局长称误解可能加剧以色列与伊朗的冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/cia-chief-says-misunderstandings-could-worsen-israel-iran-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中央情报局局长威廉·伯恩斯警告说，错误的判断可能会阻碍未来几周缓和伊朗和以色列之间日益紧张的关系的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/cia-chief-says-misunderstandings-could-worsen-israel-iran-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 23:23:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家敦促英国征收“离境税”以防止富人离境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/economists-urge-uk-exit-tax-to-prevent-departures-of-wealthy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高级经济学家和智囊团敦促财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 对富人征收“离境税”，每年征收高达 5 亿英镑（6.5 亿美元）的税款，阻止富人离境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/economists-urge-uk-exit-tax-to-prevent-departures-of-wealthy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥最高法院将审查 AMLO 的司法改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/mexico-s-supreme-court-will-review-amlo-s-judicial-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，墨西哥最高法院同意审查国会上个月通过的司法改革法案，批评人士认为该法案威胁到了该机构的独立性。这是上诉这项有争议的法案的最后手段，该法案要求法官由民众选举产生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/mexico-s-supreme-court-will-review-amlo-s-judicial-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 21:52:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
